def load_data(batch, typ):
  # naÄÃ­ta dÃ¡ta z Davinci clustra, podÄ¾a ÄÃ­sla batchu a typu sÃºboru, vrÃ¡ti df
  
  if typ in ('merged', 'coverage'):
    # merged a coverage majÃº inÃº Å¡truktÃºru - pomenovanÃ© stÄºpce a index stÄºpec
    return pd.read_csv(f'http://www.st.fmph.uniba.sk/~spitalsky3/viz-projekt/batch{batch}-{typ}.gz',
                     sep='\t', compression='gzip', index_col=0).sort_index()
  else:
    return pd.read_csv(f'http://www.st.fmph.uniba.sk/~spitalsky3/viz-projekt/batch{batch}-{typ}.gz',
                     sep='\t', header=None, compression='gzip')
    
  
def load_merge_match_reads(batch_num):
  '''
  argument je ÄÃ­slo batchu, naÄÃ­ta tabuÄ¾ky reads a match pre danÃ½ batch
  spojÃ­ tabuÄ¾ky dokopy podÄ¾a ID stÄºpca a upravÃ­ do podoby, s ktorou 
    sa lepÅ¡ie pracuje
  '''

  #naÄÃ­tanie dÃ¡t
  test_match = load_data(str(batch_num), 'match')
  test_reads = load_data(str(batch_num), 'reads')

  # zmenenie poradia niektorÃ½ch stÄºpcov
  test_match[0], test_match[2] = test_match[2], test_match[0]
  test_reads[6], test_reads[7] = test_reads[7], test_reads[6]

  # stÄºpcom pridÃ¡me vÃ½stiÅ¾nÃ© nÃ¡zvy
  test_match = test_match.rename(columns={0:'ID', 1:'strand', 2:'matching', 3:'lengthMatch',
                                  4:'matchingStart', 5:'matchingEnd', 6:'referenceID',
                                  7:'referenceLength', 8:'referenceStart', 
                                  9:'referenceEnd', 10:'identicalPerc'})
  
  test_reads = test_reads.rename(columns={0:'ID', 1:'timeStart', 2:'lengthReads', 3:'estQuality',
                                          4:'barcode1', 5:'barcode2', 6:'barcode3',
                                          7:'organism', 8:'statusCode'})
  
  # spojÃ­me dataframes podÄ¾a ID stÄºpca a vrÃ¡time vÃ½slednÃ½ df
  merged = pd.merge(test_match, test_reads, how='inner', on='ID')
  merged.sort_values(by='ID', inplace=True)
  
  return merged


def add_results_to_merged(merged_df, batch_num):
  '''
  merged_df je vÃ½stup funkcie load_merge_match_reads
  podÄ¾a stÄºpca barcode1 z merged_df namapuje hodnoty z tabuÄ¾ky results
  pre unclassified v stÄºpci barcode1 pridÃ¡ NaN
  '''

  # naÄÃ­tanie tabuÄ¾ky results, premenovanie stÄºpcov
  results = load_data(batch_num, 'results')
  results = results.rename(columns={0:'barcode', 1:'notDetermined', 2:'numMutations', 3:'Pango',
                                            4:'probPango'})
  
  # podÄ¾a stÄºpca 'barcode' pridÃ¡me stÄºpec 'barcodeNum', kde bude uloÅ¾enÃ¡ ÄÃ­selnÃ¡ hodnota
  barcodeNums = [int(val.removeprefix('barcode')) for val in list(results['barcode'])]
  results.insert(1, 'barcodeNum', barcodeNums)

  merged_all = merged_df.copy(deep=True)
  
  barcodeNum = list(results['barcodeNum']) # uloÅ¾Ã­me si vÅ¡etky rÃ´zne barcodes v tabuÄ¾ke
  
  # prechÃ¡dzame jednotlivÃ© stÄºpce results tabuÄ¾ky
  # na zÃ¡klade barcode1 stÄºpca ich pridÃ¡vame do merged
  for column_name in results.columns:

    # stÄºpce 'barcode' a 'barcodeNum' nepotrebujeme
    if column_name in ['barcode', 'barcodeNum']: continue

    # vytvorÃ­me si slovnÃ­k, kÄ¾ÃºÄom je barcode, hodnota je prÃ­sluÅ¡na hodnota v results tabuÄ¾ke
    values = list(results[column_name])
    dict_barcode_values = {f'{barcodeNum[i]:02d}': values[i] for i in range(len(barcodeNum))}
    dict_barcode_values['unclassified'] = np.nan

    # v merged tabuÄ¾ke vytvorÃ­me novÃ½ stÄºpec, ktorÃ½ koreÅ¡ponduje so stÄºpcom v results tabuÄ¾ke
    # pouÅ¾ijeme funkciu map, ktorÃ¡ podÄ¾a stÄºpca 'barcode1' a slovnÃ­ka vytvorÃ­ novÃ½ stÄºpec
    merged_all[column_name] = merged_all['barcode1'].map(dict_barcode_values)

  return merged_all


def add_period_to_barcode(df, period):
  # ku kaÅ¾dej ÄÃ­selnej hodnote v stÄºpcoch 'barcode1, 'barcode2', 'barcode3' pripoÄÃ­ta period*24
  
  # vÃ½slednÃ½ dataframe
  out = df.copy(deep=True)

  # vytvorÃ­me slovnÃ­k, kÄ¾ÃºÄom sÃº hodnoty barcodes od 1 po 24, hodnoty sÃº
  #   kÄ¾ÃºÄ + period*24, resp.  pre 'unclassified' a 'none' je hodnota zhodnÃ¡
  keys = [f'{i:02d}' for i in range(1, 25)]
  values = [f'{i:02d}' for i in range(1 + period * 24, 25 + period * 24)]

  dict_barcode_change = {keys[i]: values[i] for i in range(len(keys))}
  dict_barcode_change['unclassified'] = 'unclassified'
  dict_barcode_change['none'] = 'none'
  
  # pre kaÅ¾dÃ½ stÄºpec s barcodes, nahradÃ­me ho stÄºpcom s pripoÄÃ­tanÃ½mi hodnotami
  for num in 1, 2, 3:
    out[f'barcode{num}'] = out[f'barcode{num}'].map(dict_barcode_change)

  return out

# trÃ©novacie a testovacie sety
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(tab_all['estQuality'], tab_all['identicalPerc'], test_size=0.2)

# vytvorenie decision tree regressor 
dtree = DecisionTreeRegressor(max_depth=5)
dtree.fit(X_train.to_numpy().reshape(-1, 1), y_train.to_numpy().reshape(-1, 1))

# predict na test dÃ¡tach
y_pred = dtree.predict(X_test.to_numpy().reshape(-1, 1))

# mean squared error
mse = mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred)

good_approximation = sum(abs(y_pred-y_test) < 2.5) / len(y_test)

print('Mean squared error:', mse)
print('PravdepodobnosÅ¥ dobrej aproximÃ¡cie:', good_approximation)

def quant_vs_tar(tab):
  frequency_nontarget = []
  #vytvorime data frame obsahujuci v riadkoch postupne percentily estQuality
  quantile = [i for i in range(1,101)]
  premzoz = tab.quantile(q = [i/100 for i in quantile])['estQuality']
  for i in quantile:
    prem = premzoz[(i)/100]
    tmp = tab.query('estQuality <= @prem')
    frequency_nontarget.append(tmp.query('organism != "target"').shape[0] / tmp.shape[0])
    
  quantile_vs_target = pd.DataFrame({'percentile':quantile ,'frequency':frequency_nontarget})
  return quantile_vs_target

quant1 = quant_vs_tar(merged10)
quant2 = quant_vs_tar(merged11)
quant3 = quant_vs_tar(merged12)

def patient_to_coverage(barcode1, merged_df):
  '''
  funkcia dostane ako argumenty barcode konkrÃ©tneho pacienta a merged tabuÄ¾ku
  vytvorÃ­ dataframe s riadkom na kaÅ¾dÃº bÃ¡zu referenÄnÃ©ho genÃ³mu
  pre kaÅ¾dÃº vzorku funkcie sa pozrie, kde zaÄÃ­na a konÄÃ­ zodpovedajÃºci regiÃ³n
    pre tieto riadky pripoÄÃ­ta vybranÃ© Å¡tatistiky
  '''

  # vyfiltrujeme z merged tabuÄ¾ky iba poÅ¾adovanÃ©ho pacienta a potrebnÃ© stÄºpce
  patient = (merged_df.query(f'barcode1 == "{barcode1:02d}"')
                      .loc[:, ['ID', 'referenceStart', 'referenceEnd',
                              'estQuality', 'identicalPerc',
                              'lengthReads', 'lengthMatch',
                              'strand', 'statusCode', 'Pango']])
  
  # pripravÃ­me si stÄºpce pre vÃ½slednÃº tabuÄ¾ku
  # hodnoty pre danÃº bÃ¡zu sa menia len vtedy, keÄ je v zodpovedajÃºcom regiÃ³ne vzorky
  refLength = 29903
  data = {'occs': [0] * refLength,      # koÄ¾kokrÃ¡t bola bÃ¡za v zodpovedajÃºcom regiÃ³ne
          'sumEstQuality': [0] * refLength,   # suma odhadovanÃ½ch kvalÃ­t vzoriek pre tÃºto bÃ¡zu
          'sumIdenticalPerc': [0] * refLength,  # suma percent zhodnÃ½ch bÃ¡z
          'sumLengthReads': [0] * refLength,  # suma dÄºÅ¾ky vzoriek
          'sumLengthMatch': [0] * refLength,  # suma dÄºÅ¾ky zodpovedajÃºceho regiÃ³nu
          'sumStrand+': [0] * refLength,      # koÄ¾ko vzoriek pre tÃºto bÃ¡zu bolo z + vlÃ¡kna
          'sumStrand-': [0] * refLength,    # koÄ¾ko vzoriek pre tÃºto bÃ¡zu bolo z - vlÃ¡kna
          'sumStatusOK': [0] * refLength,   # koÄ¾ko vzoriek pre tÃºto bÃ¡zu malo G.ok statusCode
          'sumStatusNotOK': [0] * refLength} # koÄ¾ko vzoriek pre tÃºto bÃ¡zu nemalo G.ok statusCode
  
  # spojÃ­me stÄºpce do dataframeu
  coverage = pd.DataFrame(data=data)
  
  # prechÃ¡dzame vzorky pacienta a na indexoch od referenceStart do referenceEnd
  #   pripoÄÃ­tame vybranÃ© Å¡tatistiky
  for row in patient.iterrows():
    start = row[1]['referenceStart']
    end = row[1]['referenceEnd']

    quality = row[1]['estQuality']
    identical = row[1]['identicalPerc']
    reads = row[1]['lengthReads']
    length_match = row[1]['lengthMatch']
    strand = row[1]['strand']
    status = row[1]['statusCode']

    # znaÄÃ­me si, koÄ¾kokrÃ¡t bola bÃ¡za v zodpovedajÃºcom regiÃ³ne
    coverage.loc[start:(end+1), 'occs'] += 1    

    # zvyÅ¡nÃ© Å¡tatistiky
    for col, stat in zip(('sumEstQuality', 'sumIdenticalPerc', 'sumLengthReads', 'sumLengthMatch'),
                         (quality, identical, reads, length_match)):
        coverage.loc[start:(end+1), col] += stat

    if strand == '+':
      coverage.loc[start:(end+1), 'sumStrand+'] += 1
    else:
      coverage.loc[start:(end+1), 'sumStrand-'] += 1
    
    if status == 'G.ok':
      coverage.loc[start:(end+1), 'sumStatusOK'] += 1
    else:
      coverage.loc[start:(end+1), 'sumStatusNotOK'] += 1

  return coverage


def coverage_analysis(coverage):
  '''
  dostane na vstupe tabuÄ¾ku, ktorÃ¡ je vÃ½stupom funkcie patient_to_coverage
  spracuje âsurovÃ©" dÃ¡ta (napr. sumy na priemery)
  '''
  
  post_coverage = coverage.copy(deep=True)

  # zapamÃ¤tÃ¡me si stÄºpce, ktorÃ© chceme nahradiÅ¥ spracovanÃ½mi dÃ¡tami
  start_col_names = ('sumEstQuality', 'sumIdenticalPerc', 'sumLengthReads', 'sumLengthMatch')
  end_col_names = ('avgEstQuality', 'avgIdenticalPerc', 'avgLengthReads', 'avgLengthMatch')

  # vybranÃ© sumy nahradÃ­me priemermi
  for start, end in zip(start_col_names, end_col_names):
    post_coverage[end] = post_coverage[start] / post_coverage['occs']
  
  # pre sumy vzoriek z + alebo - vlÃ¡kna zapamÃ¤tÃ¡me len to, z ktorÃ©ho sa ÄÃ­talo viac
  post_coverage['dominantStrand'] = ''
  for row in post_coverage.iterrows():
    if row[1]['sumStrand+'] >= row[1]['sumStrand-']:
      post_coverage.loc[row[0], 'dominantStrand'] = '+'
    else:
      post_coverage.loc[row[0], 'dominantStrand'] = '-'
  
  # vyhodÃ­me stÄºpce s nespracovanÃ½mi dÃ¡tami
  for name in start_col_names + ('sumStrand+', 'sumStrand-'):
    del post_coverage[name]

  # stÄºpce sumStatusOK a sumStatusNotOK bez zmeny
  #   pri naÅ¡ej analÃ½ze sÃº tieto stÄºpce zbytoÄnÃ©, ale chceli sme zachovaÅ¥
  #   funkciu bez zmeny, ak by sme sa rozhodli spracovaÅ¥ vÅ¡etky dÃ¡ta

  # pre prehÄ¾adnejÅ¡iu manipulÃ¡ciu pridÃ¡me stÄºpec 'base', ktorÃ½ oznaÄuje 
  #   poradovÃ© ÄÃ­slo bÃ¡zy pre danÃ½ riadok
  post_coverage.insert(0, 'base', range(1, (post_coverage.shape[0] + 1)))
  return post_coverage


def load_coverage_of_patient(batch_num, patient_num):
  # jednorÃ¡zove naÄÃ­tanie coverage dÃ¡t pre jednÃ©ho pacienta zo strÃ¡nky

  patient_num == f'{patient_num:02d}'   # upravenie patient_num do poÅ¾adovanÃ©ho formÃ¡tu
  cov_all = load_data('all', 'coverage')    # naÄÃ­tanie celej coverage tabuÄ¾ky

  # vrÃ¡tenie vyfiltrovanÃ½ch riadkov, ktorÃ© majÃº sprÃ¡vny batchNum a patientNum
  return cov_all.query(f'batchNum == @batch_num and patientNum == @patient_num').set_index('base')


def patient_from_coverage(batch_num, patient_num, coverage_df):
  # ak mÃ¡me naÄÃ­tanÃº celÃº coverage tabuÄ¾ku, rÃ½chlejÅ¡ie vrÃ¡ti dÃ¡ta konkrÃ©tneho pacienta

  patient_num == f'{patient_num:02d}'   # upravenie patient_num do poÅ¾adovanÃ©ho formÃ¡tu
  return coverage_df.query(f'batchNum == @batch_num and patientNum == @patient_num').set_index('base')

  return fig, ax
